bilingual.source: I'm going to take bread and juice.

bilingual.target: 请问我可以喝点果汁吗？

bilingual.source: Juice with ice is also very nice.
They ate the bread and drank the juice.

bilingual.source: I'd like some bread, eggs and juice.
bilingual.target: 我想要一些面包、鸡蛋和果汁。

list.abstract: juice（英[dʒuːs]，美[dʒuːs]），英语单词，作名词为汁；活力；电能，作动词为榨汁；使有生气；使增活力。短语搭配有orange juice（橙汁）、gastric juice（胃液），例句：It uses its beak to drink juice from trees.（它用喙从树上吸取汁液。） 该单词的近义词有extract、syrup，复数形式为juices。
juice，是陈冠希所开的潮店名，店内主要出售潮流品牌的衣服、帽子、包包、公仔等产品。据陈冠希自己说，“Juice”名字的灵感来源于一部名为《Juice》的美国黑人电影。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe George would like some dinosaur juice. Dinosaur juice?
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许乔治想要恐龙果汁。恐龙果汁？

yingyinNormal.en: All dinosaurs like dinosaur juice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有的恐龙都喜欢恐龙果汁。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe George would like some dinosaur juice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许乔治想要恐龙果汁。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yes. All dinosaurs like dinosaur juice. Dinosaur.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，所有的恐龙都喜欢恐龙果汁。恐龙。

yingyinNormal.en: Can I have some dinosaur juice, please, Miss Rabbit?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可以来一些恐龙果汁吗，麻烦了，兔子小姐？

yingyinNormal.en: And now there's no juice. There's no juice for the people who need the juice and want the juice. I need the juice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在果汁也没有了，需要果汁的人没果汁喝，我需要果汁。

yingyinNormal.en: George. Don't drink your juice too quickly. George drank his juice too quickly, and now he has hiccups.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，果汁不要喝得那么快。乔治果汁喝得太快，结果现在开始打嗝了。

yingyinNormal.en: Can I have some dinosaur juice, please, Miss Rabbit? Me too. And me. And me. Okay, dinosaur juice for everyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可以来一些恐龙果汁吗，麻烦了，兔子小姐？我也要。还有我。还有我。好的，恐龙果汁每人一杯。

yingyinNormal.en: Sorry, she's not coming. We had to film them in Jamba juice instead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉，她不来了节目，改到坚宝果汁店拍摄了。

yingyinNormal.en: Juice or soda? Diet something, if you got it. Who are they?
yingyinNormal.zh: 喝果汁还是汽水？低热量的就行，如果你有的话照片上是谁？

yingyinNormal.en: Look out. Would you like some juice to go with your biscuits? What biscuits?
yingyinNormal.zh: 看啊。你们想不想来些果汁配饼干。你说什么饼干。

yingyinNormal.en: George's hiccups have gone. Here comes Daddy Pig, with two beakers of juice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治的打嗝治好了，这时爸爸来了，带来了两杯果汁。

yingyinNormal.en: What's wrong, Miss Rabbit? I've forgotten what I put in dinosaur juice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了，兔子小姐？我已经忘记我在恐龙果汁里放了些什么了。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. Hey, Jen. Could you do me a favor and drink your juice at Vanessa's, maybe?
yingyinNormal.zh: 失陪一下，珍妮，帮我个忙能不能去瓦内萨家喝果汁？

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, guys. Hey, Jenny. Go back to your room, Jenny. I'm just getting juice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们好啊。好啊，珍妮。回你房间去，珍妮。我只是拿点果汁。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, this isn't about juice anymore, alright man. Alright, so what's it about?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不再是关于果汁的事了，好吗？好呀，那么是关于什么呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Can I get you anything? Juice box? 'Naners? 'Naners? Sorry. Mom brain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 想喝什么吗？果汁？"蕉蕉"？什么是"蕉蕉"？抱歉。当妈的脑子。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, bother. What's wrong, Miss Rabbit? I've forgot what I put in dinosaur juice. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 呀，糟糕。怎么了，兔子小姐？我忘记我在恐龙果汁里放了些什么了。哦。

yingyinNormal.en: You need to put something in your stomach, William. Toast, pills, juice. That's the order. Okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你得先吃点东西垫垫胃，威廉。吐司，药片和果汁，按这顺序来，好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Here's some orange juice for you, Mr. Dinosaur. And what do you say? You are very welcome, Mr. Dinosaur.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你也来喝点果汁吧，恐龙先生，你想跟我说些什么呀？不用跟我客气 恐龙先生。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
